                            permission of the authorz.No portion of the safety plan template may be reproduced <br>
                            without their express ,written permission.you can contact the authorz @bhz@columboia.com
                        </h4>

                    </div>

                    <h5 class="ml-3 mt-3">
                        the one thing that is most important for me and worth living for is:
                    </h5>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>

</body>

</html>